-- Winthrop Realty trustees adopt liquidation plan, seeks shareholder nod
-- By Supantha Mukherjee in Bangalore
-- Tue Apr 29, 2014 10:40AM EDT
-- None



April 29 (Reuters) - Winthrop Realty Trust <FUR.N> said its trustees adopted a liquidation plan for the company that could fetch at least $13.80 per share.

A meeting with shareholders for approval of the plan would be held before August and liquidation will be completed within two years, the Boston-based real estate investment trust said in a statement. [ID:nGNXVAKHVa]